Quiz Game 🎯
A simple and interactive Quiz Game web application that allows users to test their knowledge by answering multiple-choice questions. The application tracks the user's score, displays progress through the quiz, and shows the final results at the end.
🚀 Features
Start screen to begin the quiz
Multiple-choice questions
Score tracking
Progress bar to show quiz completion
Dynamic question counter
Final results screen
Restart quiz functionality
🖥️ How It Works
The user starts the quiz by clicking the Start Quiz button.
A question is displayed along with multiple answer options.
The user selects an answer.
The application updates the score and progress bar.
After answering all questions, the result screen displays the final score and message.
The user can restart the quiz.
🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5 – Structure of the application
CSS3 – Styling and layout
JavaScript (Vanilla JS) – Quiz logic, DOM manipulation, and dynamic updates
